				\begin{document}$$^3$$\end{document} (Fig. 10), originates at a depth ranging from about 500 m to an average depth of about 4000 m, and extends in depth to about 5400 m where the density is about 2740 kg/cm3\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
				\usepackage{wasysym}
				\usepackage{amsfonts}
				\usepackage{amssymb}
				\usepackage{amsbsy}
				\usepackage{mathrsfs}
